{"tid":559684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港最垃圾食店一定係煌極！","createTime":"2018-02-13T11:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T11:46:05.000Z","uid":162177,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6a94b7c3a8692d671e84189f30e50e4952b324a6","tid":559684,"uid":162177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"小弟平時很少發文，今次真係忍無可忍先至發文。<br />\n<br />\n話說今日下午同巴打一齊食飯，無意入咗去煌極<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/190026_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F190026_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6ceedc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋就叫咗三個口水雞飯<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>，一個蒜蓉雞飯<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>，一個蝦餅烏冬<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>同埋一個蛋包飯<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>食。開頭都好好地， 點知一等等咗半個鐘都未嚟， 好我忍<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>你。<br />\n<br />\n之後三個<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>口水雞，一個<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>蒜蓉雞終於嚟。個阿姨拎咗<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>四碟雞， 佢分唔到邊一碟係蒜蓉雞邊三碟係口水雞。 之後去攞起我碟雞用鼻索， 係呀！<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>係用鼻索呀！<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好無奈嘅時候，佢終於拎咗啲飯過嚟， 就咁將啲飯擺喺托盤，放喺我哋張枱度叫我哋自已拎， 嘩乜嘢服務態度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我嗰下火都嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後,我哋見到隔離枱有六個年青人,等咗十分鐘,大聲嗌咗好幾次都冇人嚟呢佢哋, 之後佢哋嬲嬲哋更加<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>拍枱走!<br />\n<br />\n我哋諗住唔搞大佢，等埋我朋友個飯飲埋杯嘢就走啦。嘩！佢杯<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>凍檸茶好似涼茶咁嘅味呀xx<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/192021_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F192021_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cd4b5573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋食完餐飯加埋等咗成45分鐘，係45分鐘<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>!<br />\n<br />\n我哋食完諗住埋單走嘅時候，問一問可唔可以分開畀姐。嗰收銀員鬧我哋，話我哋阻住佢哋做嘢，但係佢哋做嘢咁慢我哋又點樣阻住呀!<br />\n<br />\n所以我勸各位巴打千祈唔好去煌極食野， 先唔好問好冇食，服務態度咁差，佢哋幾好食都唔會有胃口去食啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後奉上我去食嘅餐牌同埋地址， 請各位巴打評評理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/192538_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F192538_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2930f666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/192556_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F192556_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=69dd1589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/192611_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F192611_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bc69ee5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c151bba3d9b875521ead4ef9abddc68d05b04e3b","tid":559684,"uid":162177,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"補上地址<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/192843_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F192843_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e36ed98d&s={SIZE}\" />"}